232
00:14:36,400 --> 00:14:38,230
First order, no spilling secrets.

233
00:14:38,230 --> 00:14:39,670
Second order, non-interference.

234
00:14:39,670 --> 00:14:41,400
Third order, be honest.

235
00:14:41,640 --> 00:14:42,910
Three Rules.

236
00:14:42,910 --> 00:14:44,030
For daily interaction,

237
00:14:45,230 --> 00:14:47,470
