Can't you knock, Cheng Cheng?

277
00:17:13,430 --> 00:17:14,520
Make some noise at least.

278
00:17:14,760 --> 00:17:15,760
Are you trying to scare me to death?

279
00:17:16,560 --> 00:17:17,920
I'm meeting you at late night, Your Highness.

280
00:17:19,920 --> 00:17:21,830
I cannot risk letting anyone know.

281
00:17:22,640 --> 00:17:23,590
I'll take my leave.

282
00:17:29,040 --> 00:17:30,070
Don't worry.

283
00:17:30,400 --> 00:17:31,310
From now onwards,

284
00:17:31,470 --> 00:17:33,800
as long as I'm here, no one can harm you.

285
00:17:34,110 --> 00:17:36,590
After school, Her Majesty asked for my presence.

286
00:17:37,070 --> 00:17:40,000
She was curious about the changes
in your personality

287
00:17:40,000 --> 00:17:41,310
after the drowning incident.

288
00:17:45,070 --> 00:17:46,310
Why are you staring at me?

289
00:17:47,040 --> 00:17:48,000
What's so bad about the changes?

290
00:17:48,160 --> 00:17:50,190
Isn't now much better?

291
00:17:51,040 --> 00:17:52,160
Don't change the subject.

292
00:17:53,040 --> 00:17:54,830
I think Her Majesty simply wished to see you.

293
00:17:55,350 --> 00:17:56,800
You're a playboy!

294
00:17:57,000 --> 00:17:58,430
It's fine that you attract other women,

295
00:17:58,520 --> 00:18:00,400
but you attract an empress this time.

296
00:18:00,560 --> 00:18:02,000
How am I supposed to win?

297
00:18:02,640 --> 00:18:04,110
Such trouble!

298
00:18:04,710 --> 00:18:07,400
Well, we can sever ties.

299
00:18:09,070 --> 00:18:09,920
No!

300
00:18:10,920 --> 00:18:12,590
That's not what I meant.

301
00:18:13,470 --> 00:18:17,000
I meant to say that

302
00:18:18,350 --> 00:18:20,160
you're as fine as wine

303
00:18:20,830 --> 00:18:22,000
and...

304
00:18:23,760 --> 00:18:25,000
and...

305
00:18:26,400 --> 00:18:28,000
as dashing as the Prince Charming.

306
00:18:30,280 --> 00:18:31,830
I do have literary talent.

307
00:18:33,280 --> 00:18:35,430
(Look at how quick my reflexes are.)

308
00:18:35,590 --> 00:18:36,640
(Every man)

309
00:18:36,680 --> 00:18:38,110
(should learn from me.)

310
00:18:39,830 --> 00:18:41,590
Since the empress is suspicious of you,

311
00:18:41,830 --> 00:18:44,560
if you propose to marry me now,

312
00:18:44,710 --> 00:18:46,110
it won't be easy.

313
00:18:46,640 --> 00:18:48,710
I am the second princess of Dongyue.

314
00:18:48,710 --> 00:18:50,430
I am allowed to marry whoever I want.

315
00:18:50,880 --> 00:18:53,590
If you want me, then we need to work together.

316
00:18:53,800 --> 00:18:55,000
Sure.

317
00:19:04,400 --> 00:19:08,400
Mo Lian Cheng, you wish to file a complaint
against the second princess?

318
00:19:11,350 --> 00:19:12,070
Yes.

319
00:19:12,560 --> 00:19:15,230
When Her Highness was recuperating
in the Mo Residence,

320
00:19:15,590 --> 00:19:18,590
she molested me and...

321
00:19:20,000 --> 00:19:21,520
Dirtied my body and

322
00:19:21,830 --> 00:19:23,470
reputation.

323
00:19:24,590 --> 00:19:25,950
I demand a fair judgment, Your Majesty.

324
00:19:26,190 --> 00:19:30,710
This is nothing but a seduction attempt from
Mo Lian Cheng since he wasn't chosen

325
00:19:31,190 --> 00:19:32,710
during the harem selection.

326
00:19:32,880 --> 00:19:34,350
It was just a ruse from him.

327
00:19:34,640 --> 00:19:36,350
He wanted to blame everything on me,

328
00:19:36,520 --> 00:19:37,830
so I have to marry him.

329
00:19:38,280 --> 00:19:40,470
He is after the prince consort position.

330
00:19:41,400 --> 00:19:42,070
You...

331
00:19:43,560 --> 00:19:44,680
But several days ago,

332
00:19:44,800 --> 00:19:46,710
you asked me to meet you outside of the school.

333
00:19:47,070 --> 00:19:48,110
Everyone saw that.

334
00:19:48,430 --> 00:19:49,800
What excuses can you make this time?

335
00:19:52,430 --> 00:19:53,160
I...

336
00:19:56,040 --> 00:19:58,680
(Oh, no! I forgot my line.)

337
00:20:04,950 --> 00:20:06,640
Since the princess is not willing to admit it,

338
00:20:07,000 --> 00:20:10,280
Your Majesty, I implore you to exact swift justice.

339
00:20:11,950 --> 00:20:13,230
(Even though we skipped several parts)

340
00:20:13,280 --> 00:20:15,160
(that we discussed earlier,)

341
00:20:15,560 --> 00:20:17,640
(but I still remember this part.)

342
00:20:17,880 --> 00:20:18,880
(I can follow up.)

343
00:20:21,520 --> 00:20:23,400
You just want me to take responsibility, don't you?

344
00:20:23,800 --> 00:20:26,800
I know I've fallen for your trick.

345
00:20:27,230 --> 00:20:29,070
Arrange a marriage then, Your Majesty.

346
00:20:29,640 --> 00:20:31,230
We wouldn't want him to spout nonsense

347
00:20:31,280 --> 00:20:33,350
and risk having Your Majesty's reputation
be tarnished.

348
00:20:33,920 --> 00:20:36,400
Whether Mo Lian Cheng has planned
all these or not,

349
00:20:37,310 --> 00:20:40,520
have you really done something intimate to him?

350
00:20:40,830 --> 00:20:42,590
(We didn't anticipate this question at all.)

351
00:20:42,590 --> 00:20:45,040
(I have no idea what she's trying to achieve.)

352
00:20:45,430 --> 00:20:46,920
(How should I answer?)

353
00:20:56,350 --> 00:20:57,350
It seems like

354
00:20:58,230 --> 00:21:00,470
the princess still refuses to
bear the consequences.

355
00:21:01,040 --> 00:21:04,160
I was first accused of seducing Your Majesty,

356
00:21:04,160 --> 00:21:06,280
and now, my chastity was called into question
by the princess.

357
00:21:06,310 --> 00:21:08,280
I see no place for me in this world,

358
00:21:08,280 --> 00:21:09,350
perhaps...

359
00:21:11,040 --> 00:21:12,520
Perhaps I should just commit suicide.

360
00:21:13,520 --> 00:21:14,470
Stop!

361
00:21:16,310 --> 00:21:19,590
Like I said, I'll marry you.

362
00:21:19,640 --> 00:21:21,190
Look at this mess you've caused.

363
00:21:21,950 --> 00:21:24,400
You have indeed dirtied him,

364
00:21:24,400 --> 00:21:26,800
but marriage is no trivial matter.

365
00:21:29,280 --> 00:21:31,000
I shall issue a decree

366
00:21:31,400 --> 00:21:35,070
to announce that the second princess
is free to choose her own spouse.

367
00:21:37,000 --> 00:21:38,710
(That's a trap!)

368
00:21:38,830 --> 00:21:40,190
(If I pick Mo Lian Cheng,)

369
00:21:40,280 --> 00:21:41,920
(it means I really like him.)

370
00:21:42,310 --> 00:21:44,070
(So this show we put up will be in vain.)

371
00:21:44,830 --> 00:21:48,000
(What a pro! A cunning pro.)

372
00:21:49,920 --> 00:21:52,000
Thank you, Your Majesty.

373
00:21:55,920 --> 00:21:57,190
Dismiss.

374
00:21:58,040 --> 00:21:59,310
- I'll take my leave.
- I'll take my leave.

375
00:22:15,830 --> 00:22:20,350
Let's see who she'll pick.

376
00:22:23,430 --> 00:22:26,880
Everyone knows that the second princess
and Chen Er love each other.

377
00:22:26,880 --> 00:22:28,350
If she didn't pick you,

378
00:22:28,830 --> 00:22:30,800
wouldn't your plan be in vain?

379
00:22:33,560 --> 00:22:35,160
You don't need to worry, Father.

380
00:22:35,680 --> 00:22:39,230
The eldest brother seems to be upset
when learning this news.

381
00:22:39,800 --> 00:22:42,680
Indeed. He is ready to get married,

382
00:22:43,280 --> 00:22:45,520
but the second princess never requested
Her Majesty to arrange a marriage.

383
00:22:45,800 --> 00:22:47,830
Instead, she is now asked to select her own spouse.

384
00:22:48,520 --> 00:22:50,710
Of course, Chen Er will be upset.

385
00:22:51,400 --> 00:22:54,000
What the second princess said might hold true,

386
00:22:54,760 --> 00:22:56,560
but her disrespectful disposition will only do

387
00:22:56,680 --> 00:22:58,190
more harm than good to my eldest brother.

388
00:22:58,400 --> 00:22:59,590
But I know he is

389
00:23:00,070 --> 00:23:01,160
loving the second princess

390
00:23:01,470 --> 00:23:02,710
with his soul and heart.

391
00:23:06,760 --> 00:23:08,880
They have feelings for each other since young.

392
00:23:09,400 --> 00:23:12,230
If the second princess did not choose Chen Er,

393
00:23:12,640 --> 00:23:13,590
I'm afraid he'd spend

394
00:23:13,590 --> 00:23:16,350
the rest of his life as a monk.

395
00:23:26,000 --> 00:23:27,280
Don't worry, Father.

396
00:23:29,590 --> 00:23:32,310
I will not make things difficult for him.

397
00:23:40,160 --> 00:23:41,710
Nice move.

398
00:23:42,350 --> 00:23:44,560
Your Go skills have improved.

399
00:23:46,400 --> 00:23:47,110
But Tan,

400
00:23:47,110 --> 00:23:49,310
are you really going to pick the eighth
young master as your husband?

401
00:23:49,310 --> 00:23:52,310
I believe that the eldest brother
is the best candidate.

402
00:23:54,710 --> 00:23:56,950
You won't understand this, Jing Xin.

403
00:23:57,640 --> 00:24:00,880
Love is a merciless one-way street.

404
00:24:01,190 --> 00:24:02,280
On this street,

405
00:24:02,560 --> 00:24:04,070
I see only Mo Lian Cheng.

406
00:24:04,920 --> 00:24:06,190
Mo Yan Chen is a sweet guy,

407
00:24:06,520 --> 00:24:08,190
but he's not what I want.

408
00:24:08,760 --> 00:24:09,520
Let's go.

409
00:24:13,110 --> 00:24:13,710
Cheng Cheng!

410
00:24:21,110 --> 00:24:23,950
All right. One-arm distance.

411
00:24:26,310 --> 00:24:28,400
Everyone else, please wait outside.

412
00:24:28,830 --> 00:24:31,280
I want to have a private moment with him.

413
00:24:42,710 --> 00:24:45,070
Your Highness seems to have noticed that

414
00:24:45,830 --> 00:24:47,560
the decree of Her Majesty hides
an ulterior motive.

415
00:24:48,000 --> 00:24:49,000
So what?

416
00:24:49,590 --> 00:24:51,190
I will still pick you.

417
00:24:51,470 --> 00:24:52,880
What is she going to do? back out?

418
00:24:53,230 --> 00:24:55,680
An empress will never renege on her promise.

419
00:24:56,110 --> 00:24:58,070
However, more troubles might come in the future.

420
00:24:59,350 --> 00:25:02,040
So you want to call everything off?

421
00:25:03,680 --> 00:25:06,280
Are you regretting your decision now,
Mo Lian Cheng?

422
00:25:10,800 --> 00:25:12,190
I have a strategy

423
00:25:12,590 --> 00:25:14,190
to solve our current predicament.

424
00:25:14,830 --> 00:25:16,920
Would you like to hear it, Your Highness?

425
00:25:17,350 --> 00:25:17,920
Speak.

426
00:25:18,920 --> 00:25:20,760
As long as you can be my husband,

427
00:25:21,280 --> 00:25:23,920
if you ask for the stars, I'll never give you the moon.

428
00:25:24,470 --> 00:25:27,190
Then marry my eldest brother too.

429
00:25:27,640 --> 00:25:28,800
What?

430
00:25:30,520 --> 00:25:32,520
Are you crazy or did I mishear?

431
00:25:32,680 --> 00:25:34,880
This sounds ridiculous!

432
00:25:37,710 --> 00:25:38,950
You did not mishear me.

433
00:25:39,400 --> 00:25:40,640
If you wish to marry me,

434
00:25:40,710 --> 00:25:42,400
you'd need to marry my eldest brother too.

435
00:25:45,830 --> 00:25:48,520
He's so going to regret this when he
got his memory back.

436
00:25:48,800 --> 00:25:50,230
He might even kill himself.

437
00:25:51,070 --> 00:25:54,160
I refuse. You will regret this.

438
00:25:54,470 --> 00:25:56,110
I am a man of his word.

439
00:25:59,400 --> 00:26:01,710
(As expected from a nutjob.)

440
00:26:02,800 --> 00:26:04,350
(I know his craziness is incurable,)

441
00:26:04,350 --> 00:26:05,820
(but I still need to do something.)

442
00:26:06,280 --> 00:26:07,880
(Or else, when he turns into the real Cheng Cheng,)

443
00:26:07,880 --> 00:26:09,160
(he'll not need to wait for lightning to strike him.)

444
00:26:09,160 --> 00:26:10,560
(He can just kill himself.)

445
00:26:13,160 --> 00:26:14,520
Nothing in this world

446
00:26:14,920 --> 00:26:17,560
can escape from this axiom:

447
00:26:18,560 --> 00:26:20,070
What a tsundere says will always backfire.

448
00:26:20,110 --> 00:26:22,230
When you install a flagpole,
it will eventually fall.

449
00:26:22,760 --> 00:26:23,880
Today, you give me your word.

450
00:26:24,110 --> 00:26:26,950
Tomorrow, you'll wish to take them back.

451
00:26:28,800 --> 00:26:30,190
If Your Highness is reluctant to do so,

452
00:26:30,470 --> 00:26:32,110
then let's nullify our previous agreement.

453
00:26:32,520 --> 00:26:34,040
We are strangers now.

454
00:26:34,680 --> 00:26:36,000
I did this for you, okay?

455
00:26:36,070 --> 00:26:37,560
Can't you see it?

456
00:26:40,520 --> 00:26:41,800
And your final decision is...?

457
00:26:41,950 --> 00:26:43,350
I'll count to three.

458
00:26:44,310 --> 00:26:47,000
One, two,

459
00:26:49,710 --> 00:26:50,160
three.

460
00:26:51,830 --> 00:26:52,710
Fine.

461
00:26:53,190 --> 00:26:54,920
Karma will come back and bite you.

462
00:26:56,430 --> 00:26:58,110
Don't blame me when the time comes.

463
00:26:58,430 --> 00:26:59,760
Deal!

464
00:27:01,160 --> 00:27:02,350
Such decisiveness, Your Highness.

465
00:27:02,830 --> 00:27:05,000
I believe we'll form a great team.

466
00:27:08,950 --> 00:27:10,800
Mo Yan Chen is handsome.

467
00:27:10,920 --> 00:27:14,110
If I ever fall for him,

468
00:27:14,110 --> 00:27:15,310
don't you regret it.

469
00:27:15,830 --> 00:27:18,520
Whoever regrets first is a dummy!

470
00:27:19,070 --> 00:27:20,310
Promised.

471
00:27:20,470 --> 00:27:21,470
Whoever regrets first

472
00:27:25,110 --> 00:27:26,160
is a... dummy.

473
00:27:31,660 --> 00:27:35,140
(Congji Hall)

474
00:27:35,680 --> 00:27:37,800
Greetings, Your Majesty.

475
00:27:40,760 --> 00:27:41,520
Yan Chen.

476
00:27:42,190 --> 00:27:45,280
You're the most considerate one
in the Mo family.

477
00:27:45,680 --> 00:27:49,710
I'd like to arrange for you to be married
to the second princess.

478
00:27:50,800 --> 00:27:52,110
What do you think?

479
00:27:53,800 --> 00:27:55,160
Thank you, Your Majesty.

480
00:27:55,230 --> 00:27:56,800
I shall devote my life to the second princess

481
00:27:57,000 --> 00:27:58,520
and shoulder her burden.

482
00:27:59,520 --> 00:28:00,880
I've also decided that

483
00:28:02,110 --> 00:28:04,920
Lian Cheng will be wed to her too.

484
00:28:05,470 --> 00:28:08,950
Both of you can look after each other
and also the household.

485
00:28:09,710 --> 00:28:10,760
(I suppose this is)

486
00:28:11,640 --> 00:28:13,950
(to cease Lian Cheng's obsession
towards Her Majesty.)

487
00:28:14,800 --> 00:28:15,800
(I'm fine with it,)

488
00:28:16,400 --> 00:28:17,920
(but Tan Er took the short end of the stick.)

489
00:28:19,710 --> 00:28:21,280
As you wish, Your Majesty.

490
00:28:21,400 --> 00:28:22,950
(I'm surrounded by two men.)

491
00:28:23,040 --> 00:28:24,000
(Why does it feel like)

492
00:28:24,040 --> 00:28:25,710
(I have peaked?)

493
00:28:26,520 --> 00:28:28,430
(Seems like it's all thanks to Mo Lian Cheng.)

494
00:28:28,950 --> 00:28:30,110
(Might as well enjoy it.)

495
00:28:34,640 --> 00:28:36,800
Both the prince and the eighth lord
bear the same intention,\.

496
00:28:37,470 --> 00:28:38,760
What do you think?

497
00:28:45,190 --> 00:28:46,160
(What's happening?)

498
00:28:46,190 --> 00:28:49,470
Why aren't you taking my decree, Mo Lian Cheng?

499
00:28:51,190 --> 00:28:53,800
(Tan Er! How dare you marry Mo Yan Chen!)

500
00:28:59,160 --> 00:29:00,520
Marriage is no trivial matter.

501
00:29:01,350 --> 00:29:03,430
Only if you follow your heart that
everything will end well.

502
00:29:03,760 --> 00:29:06,310
I implore Your Majesty and Your Highness
to think twice.

503
00:29:08,310 --> 00:29:09,230
(Mo Lian Cheng!)

504
00:29:09,400 --> 00:29:11,760
(Why are you playing hard-to-get
all of a sudden?)

505
00:29:14,070 --> 00:29:17,310
Once issued, the royal decree cannot be revoked.

506
00:29:17,350 --> 00:29:19,560
(Oh, no! He's still in love with the empress.)

507
00:29:19,950 --> 00:29:22,040
(If this carries on, it will end badly.)

508
00:29:23,430 --> 00:29:25,830
I shall work with my eighth brother
to serve the princess,

509
00:29:26,000 --> 00:29:27,400
to be the princess's right-hand men.

510
00:29:29,040 --> 00:29:30,430
Now that this is settled.

511
00:29:31,350 --> 00:29:34,400
Who should be the first husband?

512
00:29:37,070 --> 00:29:39,680
(The empress is still trying to gauge
our reaction until now.)

513
00:29:40,470 --> 00:29:43,110
(Now that we're here, might as well
go with her wishes.)

514
00:29:44,590 --> 00:29:45,590
My brother is the eldest son.

515
00:29:46,430 --> 00:29:48,640
He should be the first husband.

516
00:29:58,430 --> 00:29:59,110
Tan Er.

517
00:30:00,830 --> 00:30:02,400
What do you think?

518
00:30:03,350 --> 00:30:05,230
(Mo Lian Cheng as my second husband?)

519
00:30:05,920 --> 00:30:07,680
(Sounds exciting.)

520
00:30:10,590 --> 00:30:12,520
As you wish, Your Majesty.

521
00:30:15,560 --> 00:30:18,800
(Seems like Tan Er loves me after all.)

522
00:30:19,110 --> 00:30:20,400
In this case,

523
00:30:21,520 --> 00:30:23,590
proceed as you wish.

524
00:30:24,430 --> 00:30:25,710
Thank you, Your Majesty.

525
00:30:40,640 --> 00:30:41,640
I can't believe

526
00:30:41,710 --> 00:30:43,230
I get to enjoy two husbands one day.

527
00:30:44,000 --> 00:30:45,880
Never see this coming.

528
00:30:47,640 --> 00:30:48,590
Indeed.

529
00:30:49,070 --> 00:30:52,110
A decade-long dream has finally come true.

530
00:30:52,800 --> 00:30:54,470
Thank heaven!

531
00:30:56,430 --> 00:30:58,430
Tan Er, I...

532
00:30:59,920 --> 00:31:00,800
Tan Er?

533
00:31:01,430 --> 00:31:02,400
Eighth Brother?

534
00:31:07,520 --> 00:31:08,190
What?

535
00:31:08,880 --> 00:31:11,800
You're my second husband and now
you can't wait to exert dominance?

536
00:31:13,430 --> 00:31:14,520
In the great hall,

537
00:31:15,310 --> 00:31:18,430
I said only if you followed your heart that
everything would end well.

538
00:31:19,400 --> 00:31:21,160
Did you not get what I said?

539
00:31:21,760 --> 00:31:23,520
You churn out different drama every day.

540
00:31:23,710 --> 00:31:25,560
Who knows what's in your mind?

541
00:31:25,560 --> 00:31:27,230
Do you think I'd joke with my heart?

542
00:31:28,310 --> 00:31:31,470
I once said that whoever we are,

543
00:31:31,710 --> 00:31:33,110
regardless of the time and the distance,

544
00:31:33,280 --> 00:31:35,760
I will find you, love you,

545
00:31:36,520 --> 00:31:38,310
and marry you a thousand times.

546
00:31:38,920 --> 00:31:41,830
Never separate in an eternity.

547
00:31:42,000 --> 00:31:43,000
